(4866, 5, '2014-06-08 13:10:46', '2014-06-08 13:10:46', '<p>Full Playlist: http://goo.gl/vvE6Vt<br />6 years ago I started this channel in order to upload FFX content, and finally I get to do a commentary playthrough of the HD Remaster. It is the first RPG I have ever done commentary for and it will be long but I am excited and hope you will join in me in this epic journey. In this first 1 hour special our hero Tidus, who is a Blitzball prodigy in the futuristic city of Zanarkand witnesses the destruction of his city by a mysterious being known as "Sin"... This walkthrough will eventually be a platinum one, but up until the final Boss battle I will be focusing on the story and ignoring sidequests. Once I defeat the final boss I will re-load the final save before it and do the sidequests, hopefully resulting in me obtaining all the trophies :)</p><p>Final Fantasy X HD REMASTERファイナルファンタジーX HD REMASTER walkthrough let''s play gameplay walkthrough PS3 VITA XBOX360 WIIU WII PSP<br />Final Fantasy X HD REMASTER Let''s Play Part 1<br />Final Fantasy X HD REMASTER Playthrough Part 1<br />Final Fantasy X HD REMASTER Walkthrough Part 1 Mission 1<br />"Final Fantasy X HD REMASTER Walkthrough Part 1"<br />"Final Fantasy X HD REMASTER Lets Play Part 1"<br />"Final Fantasy X HD REMASTER Let''s Play Part 1"<br />Final Fantasy X HD REMASTER Walkthrough Part 1, This Week<br />Final Fantasy X HD REMASTER Walkthrough Part 1, Anytime<br />Final Fantasy X HD REMASTER Walkthrough Part 1, Today This Week This Month Anytime<br />Final Fantasy X HD REMASTER Campaign Part 1 No Commentary<br />Final Fantasy X HD REMASTER Gameplay Walkthrough Part 1<br />Final Fantasy X HD REMASTER Gameplay Part 1<br />Final Fantasy X HD REMASTER Playthrough Part 1<br />Final Fantasy X HD REMASTER Walkthrough Part 1, Today<br />Final Fantasy X HD REMASTER Walkthrough Part 1 No Commentary<br />Final Fantasy X HD REMASTER Gameplay Part 1 No Commentary<br />Final Fantasy X HD REMASTER Playthrough Part 1 No Commen